data.text:
“This is not What you wanted……Not What you had in mind."

After 78 shows in 27 countries the "moderat II” tour ends in Berlin on December 5th with the MONKEYTOWN fest —- TICKETS – The successful Modeselektor and Apparat merger from the Berlin Mitte born guys Gernot Bronsert and Sebastian Szary and Quedlinburg born Sascha Ring really brought the Berlin sound to every corner of the World. The 2009 Resident Advisor The #1 Live Act Of The Year" released a fantastic second album called II on August 2, 2013. Podgorica’s Electronic Beats Festival (12-09-2014) just released a brilliant 1080p HD LIVE performance video — Enjoy watching MODERAT perform “Rusty Nails”, “Versions’” & “Les Grandes Marches” in 1080p — Also recommend the live Prague Electronic Beats performance from March 2014 — WATCH HERE
